## 🚀 Usage

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run analyzer on a PCAP file
python bank_traffic_analyzer.py --input samples/bank_traffic.pcap --output results/report.json

# With custom threshold
python bank_traffic_analyzer.py --input samples/bank_traffic.pcap --threshold 50
```

## 📊 Detection Capabilities

| Detection Type | Trigger Condition | Severity |
|---|---|---|
| Port Scan | >100 SYN packets from single IP in 10s | 🔴 HIGH |
| Large Transfer | >10MB outbound to single IP | 🔴 HIGH |
| Off-Hours Traffic | Transactions between 2 AM – 5 AM | 🟡 MEDIUM |
| Unusual Port Access | Non-standard port access (not 80/443/22) | 🟡 MEDIUM |
| Foreign IP | Source IP from outside India | 🟡 MEDIUM |
| Protocol Anomaly | Unencrypted data on HTTPS port | 🟠 HIGH |

